1
00:00:26,740 --> 00:00:29,730
♪Memory is like reflection in the mirror♪

2
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:32,790
♪Ephemeral yet lasting in the heart♪

3
00:00:32,790 --> 00:00:36,110
♪I let go of worries and face the road ahead♪

4
00:00:36,110 --> 00:00:39,410
♪The vast land stretches far and wide♪

5
00:00:39,410 --> 00:00:42,400
♪My heart remains strong, spirit unbroken♪

6
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:45,540
♪May this life remain unscathed,
till we meet again♪

7
00:00:45,540 --> 00:00:48,880
♪With calm laughter, I vanquish evil♪

8
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:52,030
♪Together, we walk through life hand in hand♪

9
00:00:52,190 --> 00:00:55,480
♪Dust rises♪

10
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:58,280
♪The melody continues amidst the turmoil♪

11
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:02,910
♪We stand firm in the wind side by side♪

12
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:06,740
♪I dream as if all is but a fleeting moment♪

13
00:01:06,740 --> 00:01:09,180
♪Yet life rarely follows our desires♪

14
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:15,520
♪With the totem of strength,
I endure many trials♪

15
00:01:15,890 --> 00:01:19,460
♪Cross love and hate, life and death♪

16
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:22,240
♪We fight with heads held high♪

17
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:26,040
♪Facing the chasm of life♪

18
00:01:26,290 --> 00:01:30,610
♪We stand tall fearlessly♪

19
00:01:30,860 --> 00:01:35,980
=Fateful Love=

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,980
=Episode 19=

21
00:01:39,510 --> 00:01:41,270
My spy has reported back.

22
00:01:41,270 --> 00:01:43,160
Beiyue is perfectly fine.

23
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,000
What?

24
00:01:44,190 --> 00:01:45,680
It's absolutely true.

25
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,590
Not only did he go to Liuxian Island,

26
00:01:47,590 --> 00:01:48,870
he also revealed his identity

27
00:01:48,870 --> 00:01:50,970
and made a grand appearance
at the Qin Gathering in Qinse Valley.

28
00:01:51,510 --> 00:01:52,720
Jun Beiyue

29
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,140
deceived us so badly before.

30
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:56,720
We all thought he was recuperating
at the Mansion of Fourth Prince.

31
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,040
But he was actually...

32
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:58,880
Mother,

33
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,500
it should be reported to Father.

34
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:03,750
Indeed.

35
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:04,700
Han Ziqing

36
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:06,760
repeatedly used the excuse
that Jun Beiyue was recuperating

37
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:09,110
to prevent His Majesty
from entering their mansion.

38
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,480
This is a crime of deceiving the king.

39
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:10,920
Yes.

40
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,800
Alright.

41
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,130
I will go and inform your father now.

42
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,570
Let's see what they'll explain.

43
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:19,290
This game,

44
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,370
you are going to lose again.

45
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:25,180
Not necessarily.

46
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:28,510
Your Majesty.

47
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:29,880
Your Majesty.

48
00:02:30,230 --> 00:02:31,160
Your Majesty.

49
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,220
I have something important to...

50
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,130
Greetings, Prince An.

51
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,040
Queen,

52
00:02:46,530 --> 00:02:47,550
what is it?

53
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:49,800
Well...

54
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,650
Jun Beiyue

55
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:52,950
- is...
- By the way,

56
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,800
Your Majesty,

57
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:57,320
there is something

58
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,770
I forgot to report to you.

59
00:02:59,710 --> 00:03:01,260
Brother, what is it?

60
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,420
Beiyue

61
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,110
is not at the Mansion of Fourth Prince.

62
00:03:13,510 --> 00:03:15,010
Then where is he?

63
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:18,990
Beiyue was seriously injured,

64
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:20,550
and last month

65
00:03:20,550 --> 00:03:22,180
he was sent to Liuxian Island
to recuperate.

66
00:03:23,270 --> 00:03:24,620
Now his health has greatly improved,

67
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:27,700
and he has just sent the news back.

68
00:03:28,990 --> 00:03:30,290
Since it's a serious situation,

69
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,750
the Fourth Princess

70
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:33,930
only told me this.

71
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:37,320
Now, I am telling you.

72
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,700
It shouldn't be too late, right?

73
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,700
Beiyue is on Liuxian Island.

74
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:50,020
Why

75
00:03:50,070 --> 00:03:52,720
didn't he tell me?

76
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:56,270
Brother, I sent people
to his mansion every day,

77
00:03:56,270 --> 00:03:58,260
but they were all turned away at the door.

78
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:01,670
He was showing no respect to me.

79
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:02,720
Indeed.

80
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,910
How can Fourth Prince
and Fourth Princess do this?

81
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:05,910
Seriously speaking,

82
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,670
it's a crime of deceiving the king.

83
00:04:07,670 --> 00:04:08,650
Queen,

84
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:11,570
watch your words.

85
00:04:14,070 --> 00:04:16,300
The Fourth Prince is a crucial figure
to the nation.

86
00:04:17,030 --> 00:04:18,390
How could his injury

87
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:20,300
be easily known to others?

88
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:23,300
If it were discovered by enemy nations,

89
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:26,450
how great a crisis would it pose
to our Tianque?

90
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:28,580
You are aware of this, aren't you?

91
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,820
The Fourth Princess

92
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:35,950
was considering the safety of Tianque,

93
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,650
so she did not publicize it.

94
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:40,580
How can you say it's the crime
of deceiving the king?

95
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,470
Moreover,

96
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:47,540
now Beiyue

97
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,600
is out of danger and safe,

98
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,980
which is a great blessing.

99
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:53,820
If Your Majesty were to blame,

100
00:04:54,910 --> 00:04:56,490
it would be unreasonable.

101
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:00,790
Brother,

102
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,300
you are overthinking it.

103
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:05,320
I

104
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:08,000
have no intention of blaming anyone.

105
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,930
You did the right thing.

106
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,370
Let's get back to our chess game.

107
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,480
Here.

108
00:05:32,910 --> 00:05:33,750
Mother,

109
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,420
what did Father say about Beiyue's crime?

110
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,270
It's all because of Prince An.

111
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,670
With his sophistry,

112
00:05:40,670 --> 00:05:42,350
the Fourth Prince is not only innocent,

113
00:05:42,350 --> 00:05:44,170
but has contributed
to protecting Tianque.

114
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,480
His Majesty is afraid of Prince An.

115
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,330
What else can he say?

116
00:05:49,230 --> 00:05:50,070
Mother, calm down.

117
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:57,820
Fine.

118
00:05:58,510 --> 00:05:59,970
With Beiyue's abilities,

119
00:05:59,970 --> 00:06:01,070
it's difficult to bring him down

120
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:02,490
with this matter.

121
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,160
However,

122
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,260
the message we sent to Consort Qin

123
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:08,930
should be arriving soon, right?

124
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,400
Yes.

125
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:14,390
As long as there is movement
from Nanzhao,

126
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:15,860
we don't need to rush

127
00:06:17,030 --> 00:06:18,650
but to wait and watch the show.

128
00:06:23,140 --> 00:06:26,860
(Nanzhao Palace)

129
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:33,330
About the matter the Queen of Tianque
mentioned in the letter,

130
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:35,210
I wonder what's your idea, Your Majesty?

131
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:38,210
If Han Ziqing is truly immune
to all poisons,

132
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:40,610
we have to take it seriously.

133
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,230
The Islanders can wreak havoc
in the world.

134
00:06:43,230 --> 00:06:44,170
If there is any suspicion,

135
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,260
it is better to kill mistakenly
than to let go.

136
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,540
But she is the Fourth Princess
of Tianque.

137
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,550
If we act rashly against her,

138
00:06:50,550 --> 00:06:51,770
it might cause

139
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:53,330
too much trouble.

140
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:57,050
If she is truly an Islander,

141
00:06:57,470 --> 00:06:58,820
regardless of her identity,

142
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,610
she must be killed without mercy.

143
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:03,880
However,

144
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,510
Jun Beiyue
holds significant military power,

145
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,580
and has a renowned reputation.

146
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,980
If we make a move against his people...

147
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,240
Forget it.

148
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:19,870
We

149
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,700
can't be rash.

150
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,260
We need to plan carefully.

151
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,520
Your Majesty,

152
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,300
I have an idea.

153
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:31,140
What is it? Tell me.

154
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:33,670
It happens
to be the Nanzhao Celebration.

155
00:07:33,670 --> 00:07:34,860
We have to get prepared for that.

156
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:37,110
Why don't we take advantage
of this grand event

157
00:07:37,110 --> 00:07:38,420
to invite her here?

158
00:07:39,350 --> 00:07:40,190
Then...

159
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,650
We'll reach the Manor in an hour.

160
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,440
Let's speed up

161
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,830
while it's still daylight.

162
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,110
Alright, Father.

163
00:08:02,110 --> 00:08:03,440
When no one is looking,

164
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,300
sneak away quietly.

165
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:05,830
Young Master Bai is waiting for you

166
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:06,670
at the birch forest ahead.

167
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:07,910
Young Master Bai?

168
00:08:08,470 --> 00:08:09,310
What is it for?

169
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,110
I'm just here to deliver the message.

170
00:08:14,110 --> 00:08:15,490
How would I know your private matters?

171
00:08:15,910 --> 00:08:16,750
Hurry up and go.

172
00:08:30,190 --> 00:08:32,330
Jiang Chen is so undisciplined.

173
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:35,500
Don't blame us
for giving him a hard time.

174
00:08:36,380 --> 00:08:37,660
Just the right opportunity

175
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:39,540
to clean up

176
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:40,860
for my master.

177
00:08:47,260 --> 00:08:48,100
Beiyue,

178
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:48,940
come on.

179
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:50,710
You're back.

180
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:53,060
Honey.

181
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:54,990
Bei…

182
00:08:56,950 --> 00:08:57,790
Nianbei,

183
00:08:58,050 --> 00:08:59,620
you finally woke up.

184
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,460
Mrs. Lu,

185
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,490
Beiyue's identity has been revealed.

186
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,500
No need to use an alias anymore.

187
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:06,020
Is that so?

188
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,240
Beiyue,

189
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:09,580
it's great

190
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:10,860
that you woke up.

191
00:09:11,420 --> 00:09:12,260
Thank you

192
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:13,820
for taking care of me these days.

193
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:14,660
I'm

194
00:09:15,380 --> 00:09:16,660
- deeply grateful.
- No, no.

195
00:09:17,020 --> 00:09:18,740
We're families. No need for formalities.

196
00:09:19,860 --> 00:09:20,860
Master,

197
00:09:20,860 --> 00:09:22,020
why didn't you tell me

198
00:09:22,020 --> 00:09:23,780
such a great event earlier?

199
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:24,860
Look,

200
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:26,140
they just returned,

201
00:09:26,140 --> 00:09:28,580
and Beiyue was eager to see you.

202
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:30,540
Beiyue's recovery

203
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:32,900
is a blessing for Tianque,

204
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:34,300
and also a blessing for the Lu Family.

205
00:09:35,060 --> 00:09:35,900
Someone,

206
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:37,620
set up a banquet immediately.

207
00:09:37,620 --> 00:09:38,660
Tonight,

208
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:40,910
we'll celebrate heartily.

209
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:42,180
Father, Mother.

210
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:46,180
You're awake?

211
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,260
Meiting,

212
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:50,340
this is the Fourth Prince.

213
00:09:50,340 --> 00:09:51,220
Come and pay your respects.

214
00:09:52,380 --> 00:09:53,300
The Fourth Prince?

215
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:55,300
Beiyue

216
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:56,940
is the Fourth Prince of Tianque.

217
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:58,380
Years ago,

218
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:00,780
when I was traveling in Tianque,

219
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:03,500
we became master and disciple.

220
00:10:03,980 --> 00:10:06,220
I even taught him

221
00:10:06,220 --> 00:10:07,180
our Lu's internal arts.

222
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,700
So, I have been keeping these things

223
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:11,140
from you all,

224
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:12,140
and not telling the truth.

225
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:14,420
Also,

226
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:15,820
his identity is special,

227
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,980
so I was worried that some people

228
00:10:18,230 --> 00:10:19,620
might harm him

229
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:20,720
while he was in a coma.

230
00:10:20,940 --> 00:10:22,020
Now, it's fine.

231
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:23,330
He has already recovered.

232
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:26,340
So, I'm here to explain it clearly

233
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:28,920
to prevent you from making wild guesses.

234
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,820
Meiting, why are you
still standing there?

235
00:10:31,820 --> 00:10:33,420
Quickly pay your respects
to the Fourth Prince.

236
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:37,100
I'm Lu Meiting.

237
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:38,900
Greetings, the Fourth Prince

238
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:40,620
and the Fourth Princess.

239
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:42,060
No need for formalities.

240
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:48,940
Where is your husband Jiang Chen?

241
00:10:49,340 --> 00:10:50,180
Right.

242
00:10:50,180 --> 00:10:51,700
How could I forget about this?

243
00:10:51,700 --> 00:10:53,220
Father, Suying,

244
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:54,140
where is Jiang Chen?

245
00:10:55,820 --> 00:10:57,140
Didn't Jiang Chen come back?

246
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:59,540
He was always with our convoy.

247
00:11:00,180 --> 00:11:02,060
Just before we reached the Manor,

248
00:11:02,620 --> 00:11:04,380
he said he needed to relieve himself
by the roadside.

249
00:11:04,740 --> 00:11:05,820
I didn't pay much attention,

250
00:11:06,580 --> 00:11:08,540
but he might not have followed us
since then.

251
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:10,420
Could it be

252
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:11,980
that he went down the mountain
to drink again?

253
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:13,780
How do you know he went drinking again?

254
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:17,340
Father.

255
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:19,140
You should send some people
to look for him.

256
00:11:20,140 --> 00:11:21,620
Jiang Chen

257
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:23,420
didn't come back and didn't tell anyone.

258
00:11:24,260 --> 00:11:25,660
He is really undisciplined.

259
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:26,940
Mother,

260
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:29,460
Jiang Chen would not
stay outside without a reason.

261
00:11:29,460 --> 00:11:31,580
Don't wrong him.

262
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,000
Maybe when he relieved himself,

263
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,820
he was accidentally bitten
by some snakes or insects?

264
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:37,140
Shut up.

265
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:39,380
Why do you always curse him?

266
00:11:39,380 --> 00:11:40,940
Can't you wish us well?

267
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:43,460
I was just joking.

268
00:11:43,460 --> 00:11:44,460
Why take it seriously?

269
00:11:44,460 --> 00:11:46,380
You were cursing your brother-in-law.

270
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:47,340
How can I not be anxious?

271
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:48,700
You two, enough.

272
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:49,540
Stop arguing.

273
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:51,180
Butler.

274
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:53,820
- Master.
- Go and call some people

275
00:11:53,820 --> 00:11:55,940
to search the mountain and the forest

276
00:11:55,940 --> 00:11:57,940
to look for Jiang Chen.

277
00:11:58,980 --> 00:11:59,820
Yes.

278
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:05,980
Father, Mother.

279
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:06,980
Here we are.

280
00:12:06,980 --> 00:12:08,880
- What's going on? Why are you shouting?
- What's the matter?

281
00:12:09,370 --> 00:12:10,700
Is Jiang Chen back?

282
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:12,980
No. Jiang Chen didn't come back
all night.

283
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:14,180
It's my parents-in-law.

284
00:12:14,180 --> 00:12:15,700
They went to the Bai Family
to ask for him.

