00:22:28,220 --> 00:22:29,380
Father, I can't leave.

569
00:22:29,380 --> 00:22:30,980
I am a member of the Lu Family, Father.

570
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:32,940
- Father.
- Master.

571
00:22:32,940 --> 00:22:34,180
Mother, please plead with Father for me.

572
00:22:34,180 --> 00:22:35,020
Mother.

573
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:35,980
Father, Mother.

574
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:37,620
Mother, you love me the most.

575
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:41,180
Master, the child is young
and does it wrong.

576
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:42,020
This time,

577
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:44,980
please give her another chance.

578
00:22:44,980 --> 00:22:47,540
She has disregarded human lives repeatedly

579
00:22:47,540 --> 00:22:49,340
and has already made a grave mistake.

580
00:22:49,340 --> 00:22:50,620
If this continues,

581
00:22:50,620 --> 00:22:53,060
she will bring disaster to the Lu Family.

582
00:22:53,060 --> 00:22:55,780
- Master.
- I know my mistake, Father.

583
00:22:56,980 --> 00:22:59,580
- I truly know my mistake, Father.
- Stop slapping.

584
00:23:00,340 --> 00:23:02,100
I know my mistake.

585
00:23:02,100 --> 00:23:04,180
Don't blame me for being harsh.

586
00:23:04,180 --> 00:23:06,460
Please forgive me, Father.

587
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,580
- If we
- I will never do it again, Father.

588
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:09,900
don't handle it this way,

589
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:12,860
it would be unfair to Beiyue.

590
00:23:12,860 --> 00:23:14,900
I will never do that again, Father.

591
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:15,740
You should leave.

592
00:23:16,110 --> 00:23:16,980
- Master.
- Leave.

593
00:23:16,980 --> 00:23:19,180
- I won't leave.
- Don't show up at the Manor again.

594
00:23:19,180 --> 00:23:20,420
- I won't leave, Father.
- Master.

595
00:23:20,420 --> 00:23:21,580
- Someone, come here.
- I won't leave.

596
00:23:21,580 --> 00:23:23,100
Please forgive me, Father.

597
00:23:23,100 --> 00:23:24,780
Pack up Miss Suying's belongings.

598
00:23:24,780 --> 00:23:25,940
- Father.
- Take her down the mountain.

599
00:23:25,940 --> 00:23:27,300
- Father.
- Suying.

600
00:23:27,300 --> 00:23:28,260
Father, I won't leave.

601
00:23:28,260 --> 00:23:29,380
Father.

602
00:23:29,380 --> 00:23:30,610
- Mother.
- Suying.

603
00:23:30,780 --> 00:23:32,100
- I won't leave.
- Master.

604
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,580
Father. Father!

605
00:23:33,580 --> 00:23:34,440
Master.

606
00:23:38,660 --> 00:23:39,500
Father.

607
00:23:41,980 --> 00:23:43,180
- Father.
- Don't call me Father.

608
00:23:44,300 --> 00:23:45,220
I am not your father.

609
00:23:46,300 --> 00:23:47,140
Meiting,

610
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:48,580
say something.

611
00:23:50,580 --> 00:23:51,420
Mother.

612
00:23:51,980 --> 00:23:52,820
Father.

613
00:23:52,940 --> 00:23:53,820
I was wrong.

614
00:23:55,620 --> 00:23:56,460
Father,

615
00:23:58,780 --> 00:24:00,860
what will you deal with Jiang Chen?

616
00:24:01,900 --> 00:24:02,860
I won't deal with him.

617
00:24:04,140 --> 00:24:05,180
After this incident,

618
00:24:06,580 --> 00:24:08,460
you should have seen his true colors.

619
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:10,260
Quickly break with him,

620
00:24:10,900 --> 00:24:11,740
otherwise

621
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:13,940
you will go back to the Jiang Family
with him.

622
00:24:14,860 --> 00:24:15,700
Meiting.

623
00:24:16,140 --> 00:24:16,980
Meiting.

624
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:18,100
Father,

625
00:24:18,740 --> 00:24:20,420
what do you mean by this?

626
00:24:21,260 --> 00:24:22,100
Master,

627
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:24,300
you just drove Suying away,

628
00:24:24,300 --> 00:24:26,140
and now you want to drive them away too?

629
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:27,060
Master,

630
00:24:27,500 --> 00:24:29,540
do you still want me to live?

631
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:32,100
Father. Meiting, say something.

632
00:24:32,100 --> 00:24:33,060
She can stay,

633
00:24:38,140 --> 00:24:39,100
but you must divorce.

634
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:40,900
- Remember.
- Meiting.

635
00:24:40,900 --> 00:24:43,300
From now on, the Lu Family
and the Jiang Family

636
00:24:43,300 --> 00:24:45,020
should not have any connection.

637
00:24:45,660 --> 00:24:46,500
Otherwise,

638
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:48,460
you can go back to the Jiang Family
with him.

639
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:50,140
Meiting, please say something for me

640
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:51,340
to plead with Father.

641
00:24:51,340 --> 00:24:52,180
Jiang Chen,

642
00:24:52,740 --> 00:24:54,220
I will not go back to the Jiang Family
with you.

643
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:55,540
We will divorce.

644
00:24:57,740 --> 00:24:59,700
You can live with whoever you want.

645
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:04,140
Divorce?

646
00:25:04,620 --> 00:25:05,580
You wish.

647
00:25:07,540 --> 00:25:08,700
I am

648
00:25:08,700 --> 00:25:09,580
not someone the Lu Family

649
00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:11,340
can summon and dismiss at will.

650
00:25:13,580 --> 00:25:14,980
If the Lu Family wants to drive me away,

651
00:25:14,980 --> 00:25:16,540
I will take you with me

652
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:17,780
and then torment you.

653
00:25:17,780 --> 00:25:18,620
Just you wait.

654
00:25:21,340 --> 00:25:22,780
Jun...

655
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:30,580
Quickly.

656
00:25:37,820 --> 00:25:39,420
Father...

657
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:40,500
I am not your father.

658
00:25:50,860 --> 00:25:55,260
(Divorce Certificate)

659
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:02,660
Father...

660
00:26:02,660 --> 00:26:04,180
Master Lu,

661
00:26:04,540 --> 00:26:05,580
I have signed it.

662
00:26:10,620 --> 00:26:11,460
However,

663
00:26:12,220 --> 00:26:15,180
I have worked hard for the Lu Family
for over ten years.

664
00:26:15,180 --> 00:26:16,820
When I leave,

665
00:26:16,820 --> 00:26:17,740
could you

666
00:26:17,740 --> 00:26:19,300
give me some land and silk?

667
00:26:20,180 --> 00:26:21,020
You...

668
00:26:28,900 --> 00:26:29,740
Get out.

669
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:32,620
You...

670
00:26:38,460 --> 00:26:40,620
I truly feel sorry for Master Lu.

671
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:43,100
I know,

672
00:26:43,740 --> 00:26:45,300
you didn't want it to end this way.

673
00:26:46,620 --> 00:26:48,340
If they have
a nice father-daughter relationship,

674
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:49,580
and the family was thriving,

675
00:26:50,140 --> 00:26:51,700
you wouldn't have to
deal with this mess, right?

676
00:26:54,180 --> 00:26:55,660
But it concerns my master,

677
00:26:56,160 --> 00:26:57,100
and since I encountered it,

678
00:26:58,020 --> 00:26:58,860
I cannot ignore it.

679
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:00,540
Yes.

680
00:27:01,620 --> 00:27:03,540
Master Lu has been very kind to you.

681
00:27:04,180 --> 00:27:05,020
I think

682
00:27:05,420 --> 00:27:06,580
what you did is right.

683
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:20,020
(Lu Manor)

684
00:27:20,020 --> 00:27:20,860
Beiyue,

685
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:23,620
are you really completely fine now?

686
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:25,380
I'm fine, Master.

687
00:27:26,420 --> 00:27:27,260
Beiyue,

688
00:27:27,820 --> 00:27:29,020
once you leave,

689
00:27:30,100 --> 00:27:32,980
we don't know when we will meet again.

690
00:27:34,740 --> 00:27:35,700
Master Lu, don't worry.

691
00:27:36,140 --> 00:27:37,300
As long as the Lu Family needs us,

692
00:27:37,780 --> 00:27:38,980
we will come back immediately,

693
00:27:38,980 --> 00:27:39,940
and do our best to help.

694
00:27:41,180 --> 00:27:42,380
Thank you, Fourth Princess.

695
00:27:44,140 --> 00:27:44,980
Beiyue,

696
00:27:45,180 --> 00:27:46,020
Ziqing,

697
00:27:46,540 --> 00:27:48,620
the situation in Longyuan Continent
is ever-changing.

698
00:27:48,620 --> 00:27:50,220
You must be very careful.

699
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:52,220
If you are not happy staying there,

700
00:27:52,220 --> 00:27:53,940
you can return to Liuxian Island
anytime.

701
00:27:54,470 --> 00:27:55,320
Here

702
00:27:55,760 --> 00:27:57,940
is a place of tranquility after all.

703
00:28:00,580 --> 00:28:02,060
Thank you

704
00:28:03,220 --> 00:28:04,580
for taking care of me during these days.

705
00:28:05,380 --> 00:28:06,780
I will come back to visit you.

706
00:28:06,780 --> 00:28:07,620
Alright.

707
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:11,420
Farewell.

708
00:28:13,620 --> 00:28:15,860
(Lu Manor)

709
00:28:15,860 --> 00:28:16,700
Get in the carriage.

710
00:28:31,980 --> 00:28:32,820
Let's depart.

711
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:35,860
(Lu Manor)

712
00:28:46,780 --> 00:28:53,500
(Tianqi)

713
00:28:55,900 --> 00:28:56,740
Your Majesty.

714
00:29:06,100 --> 00:29:07,020
Greetings,

715
00:29:07,140 --> 00:29:08,420
- Father.
- Your Majesty.

716
00:29:12,380 --> 00:29:13,300
Rise.

717
00:29:13,300 --> 00:29:14,900
- Thank you, Father.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

718
00:29:16,380 --> 00:29:19,980
You just returned from Liuxian Island,
right?

719
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:21,080
Indeed.

720
00:29:23,100 --> 00:29:25,660
Beiyue, you act so freely.

721
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:27,460
You went to Liuxian Island secretly

722
00:29:27,460 --> 00:29:29,500
without informing your father.

723
00:29:30,100 --> 00:29:31,420
Your father was so worrying

724
00:29:31,420 --> 00:29:33,220
about your injury all day long,

725
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:34,340
and was unable to sleep well.

726
00:29:36,210 --> 00:29:37,790
Sorry to keep you worried, Father.

727
00:29:38,690 --> 00:29:39,900
It is my fault.

728
00:29:42,980 --> 00:29:45,420
I also heard

729
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:48,260
that at the Qin Gathering
in Qinse Valley,

730
00:29:48,260 --> 00:29:49,940
you revealed your identity.

731
00:29:50,620 --> 00:29:51,460
Is this true?

732
00:29:52,080 --> 00:29:52,920
It is true.

733
00:29:54,100 --> 00:29:55,140
Beiyue,

734
00:29:55,820 --> 00:29:57,860
as a member of the royal family,

735
00:29:57,860 --> 00:30:00,220
you openly supported
a martial arts sect.

736
00:30:00,700 --> 00:30:02,180
If this gets out,

737
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:04,220
it might be inappropriate.

738
00:30:09,530 --> 00:30:10,370
Father,

739
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:15,520
although the martial arts sects don't
involve themselves in court affairs,

740
00:30:15,980 --> 00:30:17,620
their influence on the people

741
00:30:17,630 --> 00:30:18,630
is extremely strong.

742
00:30:19,060 --> 00:30:21,020
In the name of the Tianque royal family,

743
00:30:21,020 --> 00:30:23,780
I secured a ranking for the Lu Family
on Liuxian Island,

744
00:30:24,340 --> 00:30:25,980
thereby the Tianque royal family

745
00:30:26,460 --> 00:30:29,140
can intimidate the martial arts sects.

746
00:30:31,020 --> 00:30:33,060
This is beneficial and not harmful.

747
00:30:33,820 --> 00:30:34,660
So

748
00:30:35,700 --> 00:30:36,940
why shouldn't I do it?

749
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:46,340
You have considered thoroughly

750
00:30:46,340 --> 00:30:47,940
for our Tianque.

751
00:30:49,180 --> 00:30:50,420
I feel very gratified.

752
00:30:51,460 --> 00:30:52,420
By the way,

753
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:54,580
for the upcoming Nanzhao Celebration,

754
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:56,700
will you go there?

755
00:30:57,620 --> 00:30:59,100
I came today

756
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:00,860
to report this to you.

757
00:31:02,060 --> 00:31:03,740
Ziqing and I

758
00:31:03,740 --> 00:31:04,580
will go together

759
00:31:05,220 --> 00:31:06,140
on time.

760
00:31:08,890 --> 00:31:09,920
Look at you.

761
00:31:10,010 --> 00:31:11,260
You just returned

762
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:12,410
and now have to set off again.

763
00:31:13,150 --> 00:31:14,180
You all have worked hard.

764
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:18,140
Your Majesty,

765
00:31:18,140 --> 00:31:19,940
there's no need to be so polite
with the Fourth Prince.

766
00:31:20,340 --> 00:31:22,060
After all, the invitation from Nanzhao

767
00:31:22,060 --> 00:31:23,860
was sent directly to his mansion

768
00:31:23,860 --> 00:31:25,420
instead of our palace.

769
00:31:25,420 --> 00:31:27,220
It shows that the entire Longyuan Continent

770
00:31:27,220 --> 00:31:28,380
recognizes the golden reputation

771
00:31:28,380 --> 00:31:30,540
of our Fourth Prince.

772
00:31:32,540 --> 00:31:33,700
(Quite good at stirring things up, huh?)

773
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:35,740
The Fourth Prince is a prince of Tianque

774
00:31:36,180 --> 00:31:37,420
and should serve the country.

775
00:31:38,340 --> 00:31:39,500
It's not just the invitation.

776
00:31:40,020 --> 00:31:41,420
Even a war declaration

777
00:31:41,420 --> 00:31:43,380
would be sent directly
to the Mansion of Fourth Prince.

778
00:31:44,260 --> 00:31:45,260
Do you expect it

779
00:31:45,260 --> 00:31:46,340
to be sent to the palace

780
00:31:46,340 --> 00:31:48,900
and have Your Majesty
personally go to battle?

781
00:31:52,780 --> 00:31:53,620
Ziqing.

782
00:31:58,900 --> 00:32:00,140
(Wretch.)

783
00:32:00,140 --> 00:32:01,700
(Let's see how long you can stay smug)

784
00:32:01,700 --> 00:32:03,020
(once you get to Nanzhao.)

785
00:32:05,380 --> 00:32:06,300
Your Highness.

786
00:32:06,300 --> 00:32:07,780
The Nanzhao Celebration is coming.

787
00:32:07,780 --> 00:32:09,380
You just returned to the Mansion

788
00:32:09,380 --> 00:32:10,500
and now have to set off again.

789
00:32:10,500 --> 00:32:12,660
Your Highness, take me with you
this time.

790
00:32:12,660 --> 00:32:13,860
You're still a child

791
00:32:13,860 --> 00:32:14,700
and love the fun so much.

792
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:16,260
Your Highness, please take her with you.

793
00:32:16,260 --> 00:32:17,320
Without you watching over her,

794
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,300
she can be quite mischievous.

795
00:32:19,460 --> 00:32:20,300
Alright.

796
00:32:20,900 --> 00:32:23,140
For the sake of your service
to the Mansion,

797
00:32:23,140 --> 00:32:24,420
- I'll take you with me.
- Yes.

798
00:32:25,140 --> 00:32:25,980
Pack your luggage.

799
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:31,420
(West Yard)

800
00:32:31,820 --> 00:32:33,220
Ziqing has been back for long.

801
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:34,380
Why are you just returning now?

802
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:35,700
As soon as you return, you're so busy.

803
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:37,020
You don't even have time
to chat with me.

804
00:32:37,380 --> 00:32:38,900
Isn't this too neglectful of the guest?

805
00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:39,820
When I was not around,

806
00:32:39,820 --> 00:32:41,780
you were taking care of the Mansion.

807
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:42,860
You're not considered a guest.

808
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:44,300
Good to know.

809
00:32:44,300 --> 00:32:45,740
Remember

810
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:46,580
my great kindness.

811
00:32:46,580 --> 00:32:48,340
Don't worry. I'll treat you

812
00:32:48,340 --> 00:32:49,340
to meat and wine another day.

813
00:32:49,340 --> 00:32:51,140
We can have meat and wine anytime.

814
00:32:51,140 --> 00:32:52,780
But there's one thing

815
00:32:52,780 --> 00:32:54,100
you need to get ready in advance.

816
00:32:55,180 --> 00:32:57,500
I've already sent Xin'er
back to Situ City.

817
00:32:57,500 --> 00:33:00,020
But my parents have already known

818
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:01,620
that she spent the night in your camp.

819
00:33:03,340 --> 00:33:04,660
But do you know

820
00:33:05,380 --> 00:33:06,820
that all of this is a misunderstanding?

821
00:33:06,820 --> 00:33:08,740
Of course I know
it's a misunderstanding.

822
00:33:08,740 --> 00:33:10,820
But my parents wouldn't believe it.

823
00:33:12,220 --> 00:33:14,380
My father might send a letter
in a few days

824
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,260
to urge you to marry Xin'er.

825
00:33:15,900 --> 00:33:17,340
I've conveyed the message to you.

826
00:33:17,340 --> 00:33:18,580
As for the rest,

827
00:33:18,580 --> 00:33:19,660
you decide for yourself.

828
00:33:19,660 --> 00:33:20,620
I'm going out to meet a friend.

829
00:33:24,260 --> 00:33:25,100
Beiyue,

830
00:33:25,340 --> 00:33:27,540
if you really become my brother-in-law,

831
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:30,060
then not only will we be even closer,

832
00:33:30,060 --> 00:33:32,300
but Situ City will also have Tianque
as a strong ally.

833
00:33:32,700 --> 00:33:33,820
Wouldn't that be wonderful?

834
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:37,660
Stop dreaming.

835
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:56,980
Why is His Highness still awake?

836
00:33:58,660 --> 00:33:59,500
I'll go check.

837
00:34:22,660 --> 00:34:24,300
It's so late. Why are you still awake?

838
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,300
Come here.

839
00:34:33,780 --> 00:34:35,540
(Nanzhao)
Liuli Pavilion has replied.

840
00:34:37,540 --> 00:34:38,380
Look.

841
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:44,260
What did they find out?

842
00:34:47,900 --> 00:34:50,140
Nanzhao is different from other countries.

843
00:34:50,140 --> 00:34:51,260
It marked every place

844
00:34:51,740 --> 00:34:53,300
with a totem.

845
00:34:54,780 --> 00:34:55,620
This one

846
00:34:57,140 --> 00:34:58,380
(Ice Pool)
corresponds to this place.

847
00:34:58,980 --> 00:35:00,220
Ice Pool?

848
00:35:01,060 --> 00:35:02,140
You mean

849
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:03,980
this totem

850
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:05,980
represents the Ice Pool?

